episodes.title: Rep. Jackie Speier Compares January 6th Insurrection to Jonestown Massacre | FULL Interview
episodes.description:
iGen Politics team Jill Wine-Banks and Victor Shi are joined by Congresswoman Jackie Speier of California to take on the epidemic of sexual assault in the military, how our country can bring justice for women, and how Congress can strengthen the culture of our armed forces for future generations.  Then, she shares her experiences at Jonestown and the similarities she sees to the modern cult of Trump.

Email your questions at igp@politicon.com
